int MENodeInfoBox::getEntryRestrictions (   ) 
 

Get the seleced value of the entryrestrictions.

Returns:
An integer that is the value of the entryrestriciont_t-enumeration. Returned as an integer to be able to return error (a negative value).

int MENodeInfoBox::getLevel (   ) 
 

Get the level from the entry-box.

Returns:
The level, relative ground-level. MAX_INT32 is returned upon error.

uint32 MENodeInfoBox::getNodeID (   ) 
 

Get the ID of the node that is currently displayed.

Returns:
The ID of the current node. MAX_UINT32 will be returned if no node is selected.

int MENodeInfoBox::getSpeedLimit (   ) 
 

Get the speedlimit from the entry-box.

Returns:
The speedlimit (in km/h). A negative value is returned upon error.
